 news release\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"World Athletics President Sebastian Coe said the prize money is about \\\"empowering the athletes and recognizing the critical role they play.\\\"\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 786, \"end\": 801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999970441, \"rank\": 3.0361735252172524e-12, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}, {\"begin\": 812, \"end\": 825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sebastian Coe\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the prize money\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 846}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 880}, {\"ngram\": \"the critical role\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While it is impossible to put a marketable value on winning an Olympic medal, or on the commitment and focus it takes to even represent your country at an Olympic Games, I think it is important we start somewhere and make sure some of the revenues generated by our athletes at the Olympic Games are directly returned to those who make the Games the global spectacle that it is,\\\" Coe said in a statement.\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 1332, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a marketable value\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"the commitment\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"your country\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"the revenues\", \"fr